  "detailed_description": "Dungeon Painter Studio is a powerful encounter map design tool, with a lot of features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li>Tilesets for indoor, outdoor and world maps<br>    </li><li>Easy export to roll20, Fantasy Grounds, Tabletop Simulator and other VTT<br>    </li><li>Layers and groups<br>    </li><li>All objects are editable<br>    </li><li>Union and subtraction operations<br>    </li><li>Customizable filters (Drop Shadow, Glow, Bevel, Tint...)<br>    </li><li>Easy import of custom art<br>    </li><li>Sketchs import<br>    </li><li>One click D20 random generator dungeons import<br>    </li><li>Export to multipage pdf for print<br>    </li><li>1 inch, 1.5 inch & 1 cm grids <br>    </li><li>A4, A3 and US Letter page <br>    </li><li>Square and hex grid types</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Dungeon Painter Studio is a powerful encounter map design tool, with a lot of features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li>Tilesets for indoor, outdoor and world maps<br>    </li><li>Easy export to roll20, Fantasy Grounds, Tabletop Simulator and other VTT<br>    </li><li>Layers and groups<br>    </li><li>All objects are editable<br>    </li><li>Union and subtraction operations<br>    </li><li>Customizable filters (Drop Shadow, Glow, Bevel, Tint...)<br>    </li><li>Easy import of custom art<br>    </li><li>Sketchs import<br>    </li><li>One click D20 random generator dungeons import<br>    </li><li>Export to multipage pdf for print<br>    </li><li>1 inch, 1.5 inch & 1 cm grids <br>    </li><li>A4, A3 and US Letter page <br>    </li><li>Square and hex grid types</li></ul>",
